Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The threads of time are spun back together{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:28.83,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ore tachi to tomoni sekai kawari tsuzuketeru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The world keeps changing along with us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(All of us) a-su, a-su{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(All of us) us, us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:36.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Dream save us us) a-su, All of us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Dream save us us) us, all of us{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're annoying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm broken-hearted and angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So imagine whose fault it actually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Navy Surprised!\NThe Navy Headquarters' Former Admiral, Kuzan"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're broken-hearted?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it about Akainu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We need more booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite the drinker, Ice Pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, you scummy son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And what did Akainu say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"We enlisted the same year\Nand are now in a deadly battle."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"I feel a hot lump in my throat."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...you're magma!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Man! He launched an awful attack on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm one-legged now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what happens\Nwhen two admirals fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Akainu?\NDid you at least pull one of his arms off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure he's covered in scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of scars, he might know\Nthe Man with the Burn Scar, Commodore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? The Man with the Burn Scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:05:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You don't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There are four important\Nred Road Ponegliffs in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems like Kaido and Big Mom\Nhave one each...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't find...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...the other two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's another example of fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And they say that the Man with the Burn Scar\Nhas one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You just got that scar recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...that man sails a pitch-black ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:05:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And if someone approaches...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll create a giant whirlpool\Nwhich swallows you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be a Devil Fruit power user...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe he works for the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the World Government\Nhas a deep dark side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If they just hold on to one of the stones,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that'll help prevent pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...from reaching\Nthe great treasure of the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, tell me. Do you know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ponegliffs...\NI only have bitter memories with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had seen such an eye-catching\Nred stone in Ohara, I would remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...is my best friend\Nwho rebelled against the Government...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the sad-looking eyes of a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...whose fate was in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.64,0:07:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a dull story is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Commodore, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If we take his power for ourselves,\Nit'll be a considerable asset to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that, you pieces of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you all wanna go to the world of ice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to freeze all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fascinating power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chilly-Chilly Fruit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be nice to have that power...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I heard that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...you guys were hunting\NDevil Fruit power users.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What my crewmember said was ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't gonna do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I rather wanted to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna come aboard my ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Captain, are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're unemployed now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a place to go?\NWhat are you gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,After getting thrown out\Nby the guardians of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've sunk so low...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...that a pirate is worried about\Nmy employment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever you go, whatever you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll always get involved\Nin some kind of strife!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So what flag are you gonna fight under?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm different from the people in the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My brand of justice\Nis different from theirs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I trust vermin like you guys\Njust after a few drinks together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa! I think you misunderstand\Nwhat pirates are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not a group of good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,For a pirate group...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...all that matters\Nis that we share mutual interests!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're free now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kuzan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thaw out Hibari!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow Koby to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back to the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuzan-{\i1}san{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed.\NYou say whatever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let any of that happen, Garp-{\i1}san{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back, Koby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...how straightforward you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I'm living the way I want to now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.26,0:12:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to save your beloved pupil,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,can you kill your pupil from the past?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't live in the past, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I taught you to live in the moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Kuzan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who waver...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...are weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, at Winner Island...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:46.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,WINNER ISLAND, NEW WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you lost your ship,\Nyou're no longer a pirate group!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no means of escape, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The 100 pirates who got their hearts stolen\Nby you at Rocky Port...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...are still living in fear\Non the Pirate Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I bring back your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll make a toast in joy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting the Op-Op Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a truly wonderful twist of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to save him...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gotta save him... no matter what!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You really made it for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't guarantee it'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having a hard time deciding\Nwhether to sell or use the Op-Op Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It can even grant me perpetual youth,\Ncan't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Bepo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Sulong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! The moon isn't even out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! He fled to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back, Bepo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... leave my friends... behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust them, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,From the extremely cold port of the north\Ntill now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,we've always survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:18:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...none of us will die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.68,0:19:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We've overcome so much together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...don't die!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At Winner Island in the New World...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Heart Pirates' submarine,\Nthe Polar Tang,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...sank.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Heart Pirates led by Trafalgar Law...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...were defeated.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doredake hashitte kita noka{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}wakaranai mama kizuato kazoeta{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}zutto atama no naka ni aru takara no chizu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mirai wo sagashi tsuzuketeru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real promise{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:49.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hontou no yakusoku wa{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:56.29,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mune no oku no motto oku ni aru{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream that no one can catch up with{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:21:05.43,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}dare mo mina oitsukenai yume{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:11.14,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitotsu dakishimete{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:18.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}taiyou no youni warau anata e{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:25.15,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ano hi to onaji uta wo utau yo{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget even when I grow up{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:32.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}otona ni nattemo wasuretakunai{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:39.67,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kono negai ga todoku made{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dive into the Sea of Information!\NThe Punk Records Library!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Lilith, one of the Satellites of\NDr. Vegapunk, the genius scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Edison, also Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll introduce this one!\NTrafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the captain of the Heart Pirates\Nand a former member of the Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He is an Op-Op Fruit power user\Nwho is known as the Surgeon of Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He can operate on anything\Nin a space called Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.12,0:22:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born on October 6th\Nand likes onigiri and grilled fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He suffered from White Lead Disease\Nwhen he was a child,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.30,0:22:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and was forced to eat the Op-Op Fruit\Nby Doflamingo's younger brother Corazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,His disease was healed because of it,\Nbut Doflamingo killed Corazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The grown-up Law\Nreappeared in Doflamingo's presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.31,0:22:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever I do before I die...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.15,0:22:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...is all attributable to Cora-{\i1}san{\i}'s legacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Together with Luffy, he watched\NDoflamingo go down after the hard battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, in the Land of Wano,\Nhe collaborated with Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and brought down the infamous\Nformer Emperor of the Sea, Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:23:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he is a great pirate\Nwho has the whole world's attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.12,0:23:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But he clashed with Blackbeard\Nand got defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.51,0:23:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen it,\Ndonate to our research fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.26,0:23:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.64,0:23:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Driven by an ambition\Nhe abandoned 24 years ago,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.19,0:23:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Buggy bares his soul\Nin front of the Cross Guild members.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does the title of the Emperor of the Sea\Nmake one conceited?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.86,0:23:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that he is on equal footing\Nwith Shanks,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he reaches for the dream he once had{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and declares he'll try to become\Nthe King of the Pirates!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.78,0:23:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Let's Go Get It! Buggy's Big Declaration"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
